{
  "stem": "19550.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 273.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I mean, in [INAUDIBLE] for instance, I remembered that after-- after-- shortly after we finished building the camp, which is what we had to do first before we even went down to the mines-- they had-- they had halved the camp, after we barely moved in, and put women into the other half.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So if we were 10 to our pallet, then we were 20 after that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that there would be room for the-- for the women, who were also probably put 20 in a pallet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And which also had the kind of-- and I'm sure unintended result of seeing women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And seeing some of our women led a great many people to believe that-- oh, you know, the-- our women are alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Not even many people realized that if they saw only young and more or less healthy-looking women that that meant that the mothers and the children were gone.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Quite the contrary, that gave them this misleading hope.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And again, it's that primitive psychology, that elementary psychology, you know, that played on the emotions and the beliefs of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember so clearly when the women arrived that-- how everybody was absolutely convinced that our women were alive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And anyway, you know, the camp-- the camp life was obviously universally the same, with variations dependent on the camp commandant, or on the location, or on the climate.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But basically, it was the same system.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So you know, and I was in no way different in that sense than anybody else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in Auschwitz, the people who were not in what they called labor camps-- and there were some labor camps in Auschwitz, to where people who were taken out to-- to work in various installations.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There would be only some black fluid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It certainly wasn't coffee.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
